(64, 'Coraline', 'Coraline 3D, Coraline en de Geheime Deur, Coraline Y La Puerta Secreta, 第十四道門, 코렐라인: 비밀의 문', '2009', 3.95, 'Wandering her rambling old house in her boring new town, 11-year-old Coraline discovers a hidden door to a strangely idealized version of her life. In order to stay in the fantasy, she must make a frighteningly real sacrifice.', 52307, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4jeFXQYytChdZYE9JYO7Un87IlW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/hofnlIyF6bePkgQOpcuRWLvzf15.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T6iQnnHNF50', 'Henry Selick', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 7, 10),
(65, 'Alien', 'Alien - den åttonde passageraren, Alien - O Oitavo Passageiro, Alien, el 8º pasajero, Alien, o Oitavo Passageiro, Alien: The Director\'s Cut', '1979', 4.08, 'During its return to the earth, commercial spaceship Nostromo intercepts a distress signal from a distant planet. When a three-member team of the crew discovers a chamber containing thousands of eggs on the planet, a creature inside one of the eggs attacks an explorer. The entire crew is unaware of the impending nightmare set to descend upon them when the alien parasite planted inside its unfortunate host is birthed.', 705, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vfrQk5IPloGg1v9Rzbh2Eg3VGyM.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/AmR3JG1VQVxU8TfAvljUhfSFUOx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVwH0hIvV5k', 'Ridley Scott', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 1, 8),
(66, 'Inside Out', 'Intensa-mente, Intensamente, Ma-Hud-Sa-Jan-A-Rom-On-La-Weng, Ters Yüz, W głowie się nie mieści', '2024', 3.96, 'When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.', 58, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/j29ekbcLpBvxnGk6LjdTc2EI5SA.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u69y5Ie519M', 'Pete Docter', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 1, 9),
(67, 'Beautiful Wedding', 'Gözəl toyum, Una Boda Y Otros Desastres, Моє прекрасне весілля', '2024', 2.73, 'Abby and Travis wake after a crazy night in Vegas as accidental newlyweds! With the mob on their heels, they flee to Mexico for a wild, weird honeymoon—but are they in for another disaster?', 173, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6214Uk9CZZcIibI84o5DEtbhfyk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/hP3HWRujFCM2qLUYhSAJEm23ElP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3qDY7cZdqlE', 'Roger Kumble', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 1, 1),
(68, 'My Spy The Eternal City', 'Mon espion 2 : Mission Italie, My Spy 2, พยัคฆ์ร้าย สปายแสบ: คู่ป่วนตะลุยเมืองศักดิ์สิทธิ์, 마이 스파이 2', '2024', 3.34, 'JJ, a veteran CIA agent, reunites with his protégé Sophie, in order to prevent a catastrophic nuclear plot targeting the Vatican.', 779, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Bf3vCfM94bSJ1saZlyi0UW0e0U.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/iIvjwrDPQHCU4NjbbKpNs88uk6G.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6xJ1F7yFsnU', 'Peter Segal', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 1, 4),
(69, 'Hell Hole', '', '2024', 2.65, 'Far away, in the desolate Serbian wilderness, a U.S.-led fracking crew uncover a dormant monster gestating inside a centuries-old French soldier. Now awakened and exposed in its most dangerously fragile state, it tears through the men on the grounds in search of a new womb.', 71908, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/icqY4HTfrCwR4J8NqvcnGsKCp6S.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/95pOesHmENMYpyAEptSwD2EsGTf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WRxBvUN3FDE', 'John Adams', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 4, 8),
(70, 'Out of Exile', 'De vuelta al crimen', '2023', 3.10, 'Recently paroled thief Gabriel Russell tries to balance his life and mend a troubled family as an FBI agent hunts him down, along with his crew after a botched armored car robbery.', 830, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jgF5XaXnJmOgMxulhy2k1f9LNNc.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/wPNI1fd18z5TKBOK9Mv9Rfjb0j0.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D3bDpHMIqtM', 'Kyle Kauwika Harris', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 5),
(71, 'Under Paris', '塞纳河畔', '2024', 3.02, 'In order to save Paris from an international bloodbath, a grieving scientist is forced to face her tragic past when a giant shark appears in the Seine.', 538, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qZPLK5ktRKa3CL4sKRZtj8UlPYc.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/iwkWvcXcP8M4r9HLglhVEhgGyVu.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jnCefPQIH98', 'Xavier Gens', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 6, 1),
(72, '3 Days in Malay', 'سه روز در مالایا', '2023', 2.47, 'Marines stationed at an airfield in Malay during WWII get wind of a coming raid by the Japanese. Unable to get reinforcements approved, they engage in a harrowing 3-day battle against enemy forces.', 70162, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hqnfqeCILvgKGWKOut5lVdxdeJh.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/9Y9wTgrMk4G1YNPDDekNk7dybwx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYZeyTP78iY', 'Louis Mandylor', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 1, 9),
(73, 'Slaughtered Vomit Dolls', '', '2006', 2.10, 'The gruesome tapestry of psychological manifestations of a nineteen year old bulimic runaway stripper-turned prostitute as she descends into a hellish pit of satanic nightmares and hallucinations.', 686, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6aThc82WK9Ss8VR7amjIvHV4oQH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/R7QN0z6oNuGGfmGl92I0ZnfEE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QPgkNJ6iz4', 'Lucifer Valentine', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 4, 2),
(74, 'The Exorcism', 'Exorcismo, O Exorcismo, The Georgetown Project, 喬治城項目', '2024', 2.28, 'A troubled actor begins to unravel while shooting a supernatural horror film, leading his estranged daughter to wonder if he\'s slipping back into his past addictions or if there\'s something more sinister at play.', 941, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ar2h87jlTfMlrDZefR3VFz1SfgH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/8fNBsXpgMvqk75SPsZzTmIqSRxY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I1lNNd_klK4', 'Joshua John Miller', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 7, 4),
(75, 'Sonic the Hedgehog 2', 'Sonic 2, Sonic the Movie / Sonic VS Knuckles, Sonic – O Filme 2, 刺猬索尼克2, 수퍼 소닉2', '2022', 3.76, 'After settling in Green Hills, Sonic is eager to prove he has what it takes to be a true hero. His test comes when Dr. Robotnik returns, this time with a new partner, Knuckles, in search for an emerald that has the power to destroy civilizations. Sonic teams up with his own sidekick, Tails, and together they embark on a globe-trotting journey to find the emerald before it falls into the wrong hands.', 451, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6DrHO1jr3qVrViUO6s6kFiAGM7.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/8wwXPG22aNMpPGuXnfm3galoxbI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=47r8FXYZWNU', 'Jeff Fowler', '2024-09-08 12:37:14', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 2, 6),
(76, 'Kinds of Kindness', 'AND, Lugusid headusest, Rodzaje życzliwości, Виды доброты, 憐れみの3章', '2024', 3.34, 'A triptych fable following a man without choice who tries to take control of his own life; a policeman who is alarmed that his wife who was missing-at-sea has returned and seems a different person; and a woman determined to find a specific someone with a special ability, who is destined to become a prodigious spiritual leader.', 77854, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8mmpltkcG9areafsQHXaURedno3.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/dNplOw9U5IzlY7nNiaMS0JSVobp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NGOL2_mI9Hw', 'Yorgos Lanthimos', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 1),
(77, 'Unang Tikim', '', '2024', 0.50, 'Yuna, a woman engaged with her long time boyfriend, Nicco, starts to have second thoughts when she meets again her first love, Becca. Now she is torn between the man she loves and the woman she first loved.', 19384, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oDWZS6LznvdH7mZOYfCro0ISJCM.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/5r2NPZgYBB8ALBL3q4iX9AjTLJ6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Ud7ECZdMtY', 'Roman Perez Jr.', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 8),
(78, 'BLUE LOCK THE MOVIE -EPISODE NAGI-', 'BLUE LOCK THE MOVIE - EPISODE NAGI -, Blue Lock: Episode Nagi, BLUELOCK: Episode Nagi, 剧场版蓝色监狱 -EPISODE 凪-', '2024', 3.67, 'One day, Nagi Seishiro receives an invitation to the mysterious BLUE LOCK Project. What awaits him there is an encounter with the finest strikers assembled from across the country. Nagi\'s dream of becoming the best, alongside Mikage Reo, will take this prodigy to a world he\'s never known.', 125, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ae434jM5NG2kKX1rRkG5giMhpPI.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/7ks7A3mAO7twDOvBVE4cR8LaIM8.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6NCsj0anAt8', 'Shunsuke Ishikawa', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 5, 4),
(79, 'Heavenly Touch', '', '2009', 3.10, 'Jonard is having trouble making ends meet. His mother is suffering from depression, and he and his sister are forced to quit school in order to take care of her. One day, Jonard meets up his friend Rodel, and Rodel introduces him to the world of massage parlors. Rodel teaches him massage, and brings him to Heavenly Touch, a syndicate-run massage parlor that mostly caters to homosexuals.', 76946, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ory8WuAqznTE7lfopTSymHpop2t.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/9msuazXGWAyl7vhxVFU7e7Bb5Ik.jpg', NULL, 'Joel Lamangan', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 5, 2),
(80, 'Japanese Mom', 'il-bon eom-ma', '2017', 3.69, '\"Innocent face, D-cup breasts and perfect intercourse skills! Son, this is not your girlfriend anymore but your mother!\"  Ki-ho brings Yuki from Japan to marry her. However, he starts cheating on her with his ex-girlfriend in Korea.  Min-cheol comforted Yuki and thought of her as his daughter-in-law, but one day he realizes he is looking at her as a woman.  In the end, Yuki and Min-cheol have intercourse without Ki-ho knowing...', 14596, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hq1EaYIqUNrPM3QFYAbnH2UHoX8.jpg', 'N/A', NULL, 'Kim Moo-won', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 4, 10),
(81, 'Incoming', 'Новачки, پیش رو', '2024', 3.02, 'Their first week of high school. The biggest party of the year. Mistakes will be made as four teenage boys navigate a night of mayhem and debauchery.', 345, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k2ySukuAiAarLns0yttKS3jg85Y.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/azDmSHPzQP61OKHzpDJ7nXrG4QP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E_Vc11HVEYo', 'Dave Chernin', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 10),
(82, 'Transformers: Rise of the Beasts', 'Robot Đại Chiến: Quái Thú Trỗi Dậy, Transformers 7, ทรานส์ฟอร์เมอร์ส : กำเนิดจักรกลอสูร, 變形金剛：萬獸崛起, 트랜스포머 7', '2023', 3.66, 'When a new threat capable of destroying the entire planet emerges, Optimus Prime and the Autobots must team up with a powerful faction known as the Maximals. With the fate of humanity hanging in the balance, humans Noah and Elena will do whatever it takes to help the Transformers as they engage in the ultimate battle to save Earth.', 97137, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gPbM0MK8CP8A174rmUwGsADNYKD.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/2vFuG6bWGyQUzYS9d69E5l85nIz.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZtuFgnxQMrA', 'Steven Caple Jr.', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 7, 6);
