(83, 'The Super Mario Bros. Movie', 'Super Mario Movie, Супербратья Марио, سوپر ماریو: قارچ خور!', '2023', 3.83, 'While working underground to fix a water main, Brooklyn plumbers—and brothers—Mario and Luigi are transported down a mysterious pipe and wander into a magical new world. But when the brothers are separated, Mario embarks on an epic quest to find Luigi.', 15731, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qNBAXBIQlnOThrVvA6mA2B5ggV6.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/9n2tJBplPbgR2ca05hS5CKXwP2c.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RjNcTBXTk4I', 'Michael Jelenic', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 5, 9),
(84, 'Spider-Man: No Way Home', 'O\'rgimchak-odam: Uyga yo\'l yo\'q, Өрмекші-адам: Үйге жол жоқ, مرد عنکبوتی : بدون راه برگشت, สไปเดอร์-แมน: โน เวย์ โฮม, 스파이더맨 3', '2021', 3.98, 'Peter Parker is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life from the high-stakes of being a super-hero. When he asks for help from Doctor Strange the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.', 36573, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1g0dhYtq4irTY1GPXvft6k4YLjm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zD5v1E4joAzFvmAEytt7fM3ivyT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1mTjfMFyPi8', 'Jon Watts', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 9),
(85, 'Miraculous World: Paris, Tales of Shadybug and Claw Noir', 'Miraculous Paris, Miraculous World: Paris, As Aventuras de  Shadybug e Claw Noir, Леди Баг и Супер-Кот: Париж', '2023', 3.61, 'Miraculous holders from another world appear in Paris. They come from a parallel universe where everything is reversed: the holders of Ladybug and Black Cat Miraculouses, Shadybug and Claw Noir, are the bad guys, and the holder of the Butterfly Miraculous, Hesperia, is a superhero. Ladybug and Cat Noir will have to help Hesperia counter the attacks of their evil doubles and prevent them from seizing the Butterfly\'s Miraculous. Can our heroes also help Hesperia make Shadybug and Claw Noir better people?', 572, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7Md3nuV0ZprBTnkdR3OrUCEsrSP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/hU1Q9YVzdYhokr8a9gLywnSUMlN.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mqnwoB1xQtU', 'Thomas Astruc', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 6, 2),
(86, 'The Fall Guy', 'Kaskadyor, L\'homme qui tombe à pic, Le Cascadeur, Каскадер, 特技狂人', '2024', 3.60, 'Fresh off an almost career-ending accident, stuntman Colt Seavers has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job.', 629, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tSz1qsmSJon0rqjHBxXZmrotuse.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/H5HjE7Xb9N09rbWn1zBfxgI8uz.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EySdVK0NK1Y', 'David Leitch', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 2, 9),
(87, 'Underground Monster', 'Monstruo de las profundidades, 怪物, 언더그라운드 몬스터', '2023', 2.12, 'Near a remote town, the repeated dumping of toxic waste causes an underground cave dweller to mutate into a hideous monster. A construction team that is digging a tunnel accidentally disturb the creature\'s habitat causing it to attack.', 157, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lWVwWRLqpS1OaNg7KT0ZecSW0PK.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/oSJV6nAfHzyE9v6oEAXmDjbko00.jpg', NULL, 'Huang He', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 10),
(88, 'Someone Like You', 'Outra Chance para o Amor', '2024', 2.56, 'Shocking news hits after young architect Dawson loses his best friend London. In his heartbreak, Dawson is compelled to launch an impossible search for London’s secret sister, twins separated as embryos. But along the way, Dawson never planned to fall in love.', 38907, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zsvD0BjEQIIoh2PpE5X7VXmSrQO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/me5rUyfsVy6ixHpqVmmTVegHv15.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQ7iDaQAjgE', 'Tyler Russell', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 4),
(89, 'The Shawshank Redemption', 'Gaqceva shoushenkidan, Rita Hayworth - nyckel till flykten, Shawshank Redemption – Avain pakoon, Şouşenkdən qaçış, Xiao shen ke de jiu shu', '1994', 4.36, 'Imprisoned in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.', 944, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9cqNxx0GxF0bflZmeSMuL5tnGzr.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zfbjgQE1uSd9wiPTX4VzsLi0rGG.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PLl99DlL6b4', 'Frank Darabont', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 6, 3),
(90, 'Cursed', '', '2005', 2.96, 'The lives of six girls belong to different worlds although connected to each other through a doll called Molly, whose existence dates back to 1976, when she appeared among the rubble of the great fire of the San Carlos orphanage, in northern Spain', 351, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nQlq8Dp0DiYbAmybZFwp2JvS2Ml.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/3bqfwYl2wZSHxLjnVaTgXoZKQ8M.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_e56-jMfL9I', 'Carlos Marbán', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 4, 7),
(91, 'The Gigolo', 'Aap wong, Squirt Game - Die Abenteuer eines Gigolos, 鸭王', '2015', 2.40, 'Fung looks like a super-heartthrob and was bon with a special endowment, making him the high school idol. He was expelled from school when he was caught fighting on campus. When his mom, the sole provider of his family with her poultry business, had to stop working due to her back problems, Fung decides to support his family financially. And from that moment, his life takes on a tumultuous change…', 991, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v0YIyJc5EtAGciCZsvqsW2QPRAr.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/3W6ifzDqxINcxsZQypwupTPue8m.jpg', NULL, 'Amen Au Cheuk-Man', '2024-09-08 12:37:15', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 1, 5),
