(129, 'The Strangers: Chapter 1', 'Les Intrus: Chapitre 1, Los Extraños: Parte 1, The Strangers, The Strangers: Part One', '2024', 2.99, 'After their car breaks down in an eerie small town, a young couple are forced to spend the night in a remote cabin. Panic ensues as they are terrorized by three masked strangers who strike with no mercy and seemingly no motives.', 14703, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oYsCNpW4k7Pd7ac3uQfBhr2ihtW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/vvIKttfL7SoE9rZyLkg6TaAVsDH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3pZUQmZdOi4', 'Renny Harlin', '2024-09-08 12:37:16', '2024-09-23 05:14:39', 1, 3, 10),
