(208, 'The Wild Robot', 'Robô Selvagem, Robot salvaje, The Wild Robot, Дзікі робат, Дивият робот', '2024', 0.00, 'A robot — ROZZUM unit 7134, “Roz” for short — is shipwrecked on an uninhabited island and must learn to adapt to the harsh surroundings, gradually building relationships with the animals on the island and becoming the adoptive parent of an orphaned gosling.', 85473, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wTnV3PCVW5O92JMrFvvrRcV39RU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/62zw627mH74rng9zc4tFfaR54KW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hbciJR5CsBA', 'Chris Sanders', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 8),
(209, 'Black Noise', '', '2023', 2.72, 'Members of an elite security team deployed to rescue a VIP on an exclusive island.The rescue mission becomes a desperate attempt to survive, escape the island and elude the sinister presence that seeks to harm them.', 768, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/snKpXexv5dtWqEKEmXrJtp8QGQC.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/dbtGinhWWKgQLQ0hjZHMFWxBJcJ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eYdLTA6n8kA', 'Philippe Martinez', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 2),
(210, 'Father There is Only One 4', 'Father There Is Only One 4: Wedding Bells', '2024', 3.53, 'The eldest of the family, Sara, comes of age and brings chaos to the family by announcing her intention to marry Ocho. Javier and Marisa try to avoid it at all costs. At the same time Dani has an existential crisis, Paulita feels jealous of Cris, Carlota announces that she has found a boyfriend from a high society family and Rocio has finally managed to be cast in her first film.', 86, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bDXDvPQYvnh8OKA5qJEAvHtfUp6.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/nk3RLLZiRAsUxZjtZoXTu77IN03.jpg', NULL, 'Santiago Segura', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 5),
(211, 'Joker', 'Guasón, JOKER小丑, Джокер, ジョーカー, 小丑', '2019', 4.08, 'During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.', 604, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/gZWl93sf8AxavYpVT1Un6EF3oCj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-RFFRxcoKfA', 'Todd Phillips', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 3),
(212, 'Ghostbusters: Frozen Empire', 'Ghostbusters 4, Мисливці на привидів: крижана імперія, 捉鬼敢死队：冰封之城, 고스트버스터즈: 오싹한 뉴욕', '2024', 3.33, 'When the discovery of an ancient artifact unleashes an evil force, Ghostbusters new and old must join forces to protect their home and save the world from a second Ice Age.', 443, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e1J2oNzSBdou01sUvriVuoYp0pJ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/5cCfqeUH2f5Gnu7Lh9xepY9TB6x.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X7Di42uUaF0', 'Gil Kenan', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 2),
(213, 'HAIKYU!! The Dumpster Battle', 'HAIKYU!! A Batalha do Lixo, HAIKYU!! Das Play-off der Müllhalde, Haikyu!! The Dumpster Battle, Haikyuu!! THE MOVIE -Decisive Battle at the Garbage Dump-', '2024', 3.50, 'Shoyo Hinata joins Karasuno High\'s volleyball club to be like his idol, a former Karasuno player known as the \'Little Giant\'. But Hinata soon learns that he must team up with his middle school nemesis, Tobio Kageyama. Their clashing styles form a surprising weapon, but can their newfound teamwork defeat their rival Nekoma High in the highly anticipated \'Dumpster Battle\', the long awaited ultimate showdown between two opposing underdog teams?', 961, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ntRU0OA4etGGiMMmH1Yw0bnaMdW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/cZmOrIOkJ2SNfVdiO85dUbOAYnL.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jlU8bA9LtTM', 'Susumu Mitsunaka', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 7),
(214, 'El Candidato Honesto', 'The Honest Candidate', '2024', 2.50, 'A former idealistic leader turned corrupt politician is cursed by his grandmother on the eve of the presidential election, forcing him to be honest. Can he win without lies and what will be the conditions?', 957, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hmV5HPkbQuzgPo11Xm70CMQV3iZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/uFMIiNYUDHzo7YGSg5UUR7VLNma.jpg', NULL, 'Pipe Ybarra', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(215, 'X-Men: Days of Future Past', 'Iks-odamlar, X-Men Días del futuro pasado Rogue Cut, X-Men: Days of Future Past 3D, X-מן: העתיד שהיה, 엑스맨: 데이즈 오브 퓨처 패스트', '2014', 3.77, 'The ultimate X-Men ensemble fights a war for the survival of the species across two time periods as they join forces with their younger selves in an epic battle that must change the past – to save our future.', 777, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tYfijzolzgoMOtegh1Y7j2Enorg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/l53XKi0sJb83AN1BWndnMwiTqLq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsjtg7m1MMM', 'Bryan Singer', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 10),
(216, 'Breathe', 'Χωρίς Οξυγόνο, Останній подих, دمیدن', '2024', 2.60, 'Air-supply is scarce in the near future, forcing a mother and daughter to fight for survival when two strangers arrive desperate for an oxygenated haven.', 626, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wTW2t8ocWDlHns8I7vQxuqkyK58.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/sHJTUdNOxy77MfiwtVIqHxCB2W.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JENDBXIfWWM', 'Stefon Bristol', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 5),
(217, 'Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire', 'Harijs Poters un Uguns biķeris, Harry Potter dhe Kupa e Zjarrit, הרי פותר וגביע האש, ハリー・ポッターと炎のゴブレット', '2005', 3.91, 'When Harry Potter\'s name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.', 842, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/5rrGVmRUuCKVbqUu41XIWTXJmNA.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xkFJgcCQRE', 'Mike Newell', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 2),
(218, 'Megamind vs. the Doom Syndicate', 'Megamente 2, Megamind 2', '2024', 2.41, 'Megamind\'s former villain team, The Doom Syndicate, has returned. Our newly crowned blue hero must now keep up evil appearances until he can assemble his friends (Roxanne, Ol\' Chum and Keiko) to stop his former evil teammates from launching Metro City to the Moon.', 937, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1N7terrMeZPwK5qq31MUD0HQ3IG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/3Kzc6V4MWs3RXCmE5DhAYnfWL8F.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DXb7tWC2W5o', 'Eric Fogel', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 5),
(219, 'Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix', 'Harry Potter E L\'ordine della fenice, Harry Potter I Zakon Feniksa, Harry Potter Och Fenix-Orden, Harry Potter og Foniks-Ordenen, Harry Potter og fonix- ordenen', '2007', 3.84, 'Returning for his fifth year of study at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of students to defend themselves against the dark arts.', 345, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/pkxPkHOPJjOvzfQOclANEBT8OfK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=47PHbQTmw5g', 'David Yates', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 9),
(220, 'Run, Tiger Run!', 'Xiao hu dun da ying xiong, Беги, тигр, беги!', '2022', 3.81, 'The film follows a young boy who sets out on a mission to try and track down his long lost parents.', 918, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/73PZdKGTj2PkIeBfRhTG5KJBY5X.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jt86ZDWeo5SuSryi3kzaysf1CWU.jpg', NULL, 'Stanley Tsang', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 10),
(221, 'Trigger Warning', '触发警报', '2024', 2.91, 'A Special Forces commando uncovers a dangerous conspiracy when she returns to her hometown looking for answers into her beloved father\'s death.', 186, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lJN24nn28s5afC1UnLPYRgYOp1K.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/aATi2PtaOQCVAquCym6OU0Z4FjY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MnHTLh6ruW0', 'Mouly Surya', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 2),
(222, 'Dune', 'Dune: Part One, חולית: חלק ראשון, デューン', '2021', 3.90, 'Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet\'s exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence-a commodity capable of unlocking humanity\'s greatest potential-only those who can conquer their fear will survive.', 674, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/d5NXSklXo0qyIYkgV94XAgMIckC.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/lzWHmYdfeFiMIY4JaMmtR7GEli3.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w0HgHet0sxg', 'Denis Villeneuve', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(223, 'Five Nights at Freddy\'s', 'Bad Cupcake, Pet noći kod Fredija, Пять ночей с Фредди, Пять ночей у Фредди', '2023', 3.79, 'Recently fired and desperate for work, a troubled young man named Mike agrees to take a position as a night security guard at an abandoned theme restaurant: Freddy Fazbear\'s Pizzeria. But he soon discovers that nothing at Freddy\'s is what it seems.', 28905, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A4j8S6moJS2zNtRR8oWF08gRnL5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/7NRGAtu8E4343NSKwhkgmVRDINw.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X4d_v-HyR4o', 'Emma Tammi', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 2),
(224, 'Fifty Shades of Grey', '50 Shades of Grey, 50 Оттенков Серого, Vijftig Tinten Grijs', '2015', 2.95, 'When college senior Anastasia Steele steps in for her sick roommate to interview prominent businessman Christian Grey for their campus paper, little does she realize the path her life will take. Christian, as enigmatic as he is rich and powerful, finds himself strangely drawn to Ana, and she to him. Though sexually inexperienced, Ana plunges headlong into an affair -- and learns that Christian\'s true sexual proclivities push the boundaries of pain and pleasure.', 505, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/63kGofUkt1Mx0SIL4XI4Z5AoSgt.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/mgY8An5qVCgLh97KOWeJVJarskL.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6FDTMRK7-24', 'Sam Taylor-Johnson', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 10),
(225, 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1', 'Harry Potter a Dary smrti - 1. časť, Harry Potter en de relieken des doods - Deel 1, Harry Potter och dödsrelikerna – Del 1, Harry Potter y las Reliquias de la Muerte: Parte 1, 해리 포터와 죽음의 성물 - 파트1', '2010', 3.88, 'Harry, Ron and Hermione walk away from their last year at Hogwarts to find and destroy the remaining Horcruxes, putting an end to Voldemort\'s bid for immortality. But with Harry\'s beloved Dumbledore dead and Voldemort\'s unscrupulous Death Eaters on the loose, the world is more dangerous than ever.', 811, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iGoXIpQb7Pot00EEdwpwPajheZ5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/AqLcLsGGTzAjm3pCCq0CZCQrp6m.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MxqsmsA8y5k', 'David Yates', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 10),
(226, 'Tangled', 'To på flugt - Et hårrejsende eventyr, Vrlo zapetljana priča, گیسوکمند, 长发公主, 魔髮奇緣', '2010', 3.81, 'When the kingdom\'s most wanted-and most charming-bandit Flynn Rider hides out in a mysterious tower, he\'s taken hostage by Rapunzel, a beautiful and feisty tower-bound teen with 70 feet of magical, golden hair. Flynn\'s curious captor, who\'s looking for her ticket out of the tower where she\'s been locked away for years, strikes a deal with the handsome thief and the unlikely duo sets off on an action-packed escapade, complete with a super-cop horse, an over-protective chameleon and a gruff gang of pub thugs.', 19186, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ym7Kst6a4uodryxqbGOxmewF235.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/cWczNud8Y8i8ab0Z4bxos4myWYO.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hsJFEqOL1UI', 'Nathan Greno', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 3),
(227, 'The Idea of You', 'Als du mich sahst, 关于你的想法, 아이디어 오브 유', '2024', 3.70, '40-year-old single mom Solène begins an unexpected romance with 24-year-old Hayes Campbell, the lead singer of August Moon, the hottest boy band on the planet. As they begin a whirlwind romance, it isn\'t long before Hayes\' superstar status poses unavoidable challenges to their relationship, and Solène soon discovers that life in the glare of his spotlight might be more than she bargained for.', 491, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Y5P4Q3q8nrruZ9aD3wXeJS2Plg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/sI6uCeF8mUlZx22mFfHSi9W3XQ9.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pz6qx4n2Ewc', 'Michael Showalter', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 7),
(228, 'L.E.T.H.A.L. Ladies: Return to Savage Beach', 'A szexi csapat: Kincsvadászok, Eglima genous thilykou, L.E.T.H.A.L. Ladies - Return to Savage Beach, Return to Savage Beach', '1998', 2.99, 'A stolen computer disk contains the location of a hidden tresaure trove. It\'s up to the sexy ladies of LETHAL (Legion to Ensure Total Harmony and Law) to find the treasure before the bad guys do.', 213, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9z3hdYnDdfWGKD55kdDmshDojeP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/cQpSKsSjoQYnDmqTlYl0gV3qnif.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mFSqz_gfSUw', 'Andy Sidaris', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 9),
(229, 'The Last Kumite', 'Bloodsport: The Last Kumite, Su último combate, 绝杀组手', '2024', 3.40, 'When Karate champion Michael Rivers wins the last tournament of his career, shady businessman Ron Hall offers him the opportunity to fight in an illegal Kumite in Bulgaria against the world’s best martial artists.  When Michael declines, Hall has his daughter kidnapped and, in order to rescue her, Rivers is left with no choice but to compete in the deadly tournament. Arriving in Bulgaria, he finds out that he is not the only fighter whose loved one was taken. Rivers enlists the help of trainers Master Loren, and Julie Jackson but will it be enough for him to win the tournament and save his daughter’s life?', 94239, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zDkaJgsPoSqa2cMe2hW2HAfyWwO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/g5Ha2DhXIuxsUl4gaDnbw3jOAlo.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R1VeyLrVaIo', 'Ross W. Clarkson', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 8),
(230, 'Fury', 'Corazones de Hierro, Fury, Fury - Herz aus Stahl, フューリー 2014, 战逆豪情', '2014', 3.77, 'In the last months of World War II, as the Allies make their final push in the European theatre, a battle-hardened U.S. Army sergeant named \'Wardaddy\' commands a Sherman tank called \'Fury\' and its five-man crew on a deadly mission behind enemy lines. Outnumbered and outgunned, Wardaddy and his men face overwhelming odds in their heroic attempts to strike at the heart of Nazi Germany.', 47119, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pfte7wdMobMF4CVHuOxyu6oqeeA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/kdbLf3aTQsEXqYlH9vA4fzmnSFz.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09w9MTtZDEM', 'David Ayer', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(231, 'The Crow', 'El cuervo, Il Corvo 1 - The Crow, Le Corbeau, O Corvo, Ölümsüz Aşk', '2024', 3.77, 'Exactly one year after young rock guitarist Eric Draven and his fiancée are brutally killed by a ruthless gang of criminals, Draven—watched over by a hypnotic crow—returns from the grave to exact revenge.', 969, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rMMB3v6jYHjsvXRNJYESacoTD7j.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/f1JmD60vV383EDKr86lqmPB4sOu.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4CLE3pWAAr8', 'Alex Proyas', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 3),
(232, 'The Tearsmith', 'Rzeźbiarz Łez, The Tearsmith, 眼泪制造者', '2024', 3.27, 'Adopted together after a tough childhood in an orphanage, Nica and Rigel realize that unexpected but irresistible feelings pull them together.', 56, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uoBHsxSgfc3PQsSn98RfnbePHOy.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/e3gVl1gnxEFKLTF6pn6KRqUPi9K.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qEh_90RnlD8', 'Alessandro Genovesi', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 1),
(233, 'Damsel', 'A Donzela, Dalaga, Donzela', '2024', 3.54, 'A young woman\'s marriage to a charming prince turns into a fierce fight for survival when she\'s offered up as a sacrifice to a fire-breathing dragon.', 794, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AgHbB9DCE9aE57zkHjSmseszh6e.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/deLWkOLZmBNkm8p16igfapQyqeq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iM150ZWovZM', 'Juan Carlos Fresnadillo', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(234, 'Venom: The Last Dance', 'Venom 3, Venom: A Última Rodada, Веном: Последний Танец, 베놈 3', '2024', 0.00, 'Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie\'s last dance.', 613, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aosm8NMQ3UyoBVpSxyimorCQykC.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/3sh2UA2Q2l7fihgoj1LhFFPTlIM.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6XmBefPeDnE', 'Kelly Marcel', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 1),
(235, 'Cinderella', 'Күлбике, 仙履奇缘', '2015', 3.40, 'When her father unexpectedly passes away, young Ella finds herself at the mercy of her cruel stepmother and her daughters. Never one to give up hope, Ella\'s fortunes begin to change after meeting a dashing stranger in the woods.', 5028, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j91LJmcWo16CArFOoapsz84bwxb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/q7vmCCmyiHnuKGMzHZlr0fD44b9.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n44EWI92Tc8', 'Kenneth Branagh', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 3);
