(236, 'The Equalizer 3', 'The Equalizer 3 - The Final Chapter, The Equalizer 3: Capítulo Final, موازنه‌ساز ۳, 私刑教育3', '2023', 3.67, 'Robert McCall finds himself at home in Southern Italy but he discovers his friends are under the control of local crime bosses. As events turn deadly, McCall knows what he has to do: become his friends\' protector by taking on the mafia.', 518, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b0Ej6fnXAP8fK75hlyi2jKqdhHz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/tC78Pck2YCsUAtEdZwuHYUFYtOj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fQfrzHFmVe8', 'Antoine Fuqua', '2024-09-08 12:37:18', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 4),
