(298, 'Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms', 'Creation of The Gods 1: Kingdom of Storms, Creation of the Gods I Kingdom of Storms, آفرینش خدایان ۱: پادشاهی طوفان‌ها, 封神演义系列·龙之战, 봉신제일부: 조가풍운', '2023', 3.56, 'Based on the most well-known classical fantasy novel of China, Fengshenyanyi, the trilogy is a magnificent eastern high fantasy epic that recreates the prolonged mythical wars between humans, immortals and monsters, which happened more than three thousand years ago.', 126, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1v5ZteB49M0RUGYrf9R37Mz8yo2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/2C3CdVzINUm5Cm1lrbT2uiRstwX.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ucTl-cxIjc', 'Wuershan', '2024-09-08 12:37:20', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 6),
(299, 'Love Lies Bleeding', 'Amor em Sangue, Amor Mentiras y Sangre, D\'amour et de sang, Love Lies Bleeding: O Amor Sangra, Ματωμένος Δεσμός', '2024', 3.28, 'Reclusive gym manager Lou falls hard for Jackie, an ambitious bodybuilder headed through town to Las Vegas in pursuit of her dream. But their love ignites violence, pulling them deep into the web of Lou’s criminal family.', 51223, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p7jyFWiLyHPttqYBFAlLJwtYTYH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/oMiKHO3H5RixfLsiU5Vumhlp5sj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AULR_GPteNQ', 'Rose Glass', '2024-09-08 12:37:20', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 8),
(300, 'Ratatouille', 'Juhu-hu, O ratatouis, Remî no oishî resutoran, 料理鼠王', '2007', 3.91, 'Remy, a resident of Paris, appreciates good food and has quite a sophisticated palate. He would love to become a chef so he can create and enjoy culinary masterpieces to his heart\'s delight. The only problem is, Remy is a rat. When he winds up in the sewer beneath one of Paris\' finest restaurants, the rodent gourmet finds himself ideally placed to realize his dream.', 976, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t3vaWRPSf6WjDSamIkKDs1iQWna.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/xgDj56UWyeWQcxQ44f5A3RTWuSs.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NgsQ8mVkN8w', 'Brad Bird', '2024-09-08 12:37:20', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 3),
(301, 'Meg 2: The Trench', 'Meg - Az őscápa 2: Az árok, The Meg 2: The Trench, เม็ก 2: อภิมหาโคตรหลามร่องนรก, 巨齿鲨2：深渊, 메가로돈 2: 더 트렌치', '2023', 3.26, 'An exploratory dive into the deepest depths of the ocean of a daring research team spirals into chaos when a malevolent mining operation threatens their mission and forces them into a high-stakes battle for survival.', 926, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4m1Au3YkjqsxF8iwQy0fPYSxE0h.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/5mzr6JZbrqnqD8rCEvPhuCE5Fw2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dG91B3hHyY4', 'Ben Wheatley', '2024-09-08 12:37:20', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 5),
(302, 'The Three Musketeers: Milady', 'Die Drei Musketiere - Milady, Die Drei Musketiere: Milady, I tre moschettieri - Milady, Os Três Mosqueteiros: Milady, Trys muškietininkai: Miledi', '2023', 3.25, 'D\'Artagnan, on a quest to rescue the abducted Constance, runs into the mysterious Milady de Winter again. The tension between the Catholics and the Protestants finally escalates, as the king declares war — forcing the now four musketeers into battle. But as the war goes on, they are tested physically, mentally and emotionally.', 544, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rtosxP5sXuoRFPH4sVbMccLIPiV.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/qGJASuD3fs9ZBxuEZoxCLVidVq8.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzXPjLAWswQ', 'Martin Bourboulon', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 4),
(303, 'Venom: Let There Be Carnage', 'Venom 2, Venom: Carnage liberado, 베놈 2 렛 데어 비 카니지', '2021', 3.40, 'After finding a host body in investigative reporter Eddie Brock, the alien symbiote must face a new enemy, Carnage, the alter ego of serial killer Cletus Kasady.', 9561, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1MJNcPZy46hIy2CmSqOeru0yr5C.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/vIgyYkXkg6NC2whRbYjBD7eb3Er.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GVwq2HlKYpE', 'Andy Serkis', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 6),
(304, 'Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Movie: Mugen Train', 'Kimetsu no Yaiba : Le Train de l\'infini, Kimetsu no Yaiba Movie: Mugen Ressha hen, Kimetsu no yaiba: Mugen Ressha hen, 劇場版 鬼滅之刃 無限列車篇, 鬼滅之刃 劇場版 無限列車篇', '2020', 4.11, 'Tanjiro Kamado, joined with Inosuke Hashibira, a boy raised by boars who wears a boar\'s head, and Zenitsu Agatsuma, a scared boy who reveals his true power when he sleeps, boards the Infinity Train on a new mission with the Fire Hashira, Kyojuro Rengoku, to defeat a demon who has been tormenting the people and killing the demon slayers who oppose it!', 295, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h8Rb9gBr48ODIwYUttZNYeMWeUU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/qjGrUmKW78MCFG8PTLDBp67S27p.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XbTSLJ62YEM', 'Haruo Sotozaki', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 2),
(305, 'The Forge', 'Kendrick Brothers 2024 Film, La Forja', '2024', 2.70, '19 year old Isaiah Wright lives for basketball and video games. A year out of high school, he has no job, no plans, and no idea how to be a man. At odds with his single mother Cynthia, Isaiah is given an ultimatum – to step up or move out. Feeling the pull from his friends and the push from his mom, Isaiah is hired by Moore Fitness, unaware of how the owner will personally impact his life. With the prayers of his mother and unexpected guidance from his new mentor, Isaiah is forced to deal with his past, sacrifice his selfishness and discover how God might have a greater purpose for his life.', 114, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3mlyu5R8EnKst5UHPEx46meduNP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/9XDgbD365BU4cFyyhLZIgyUYSId.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s4aCsaDvagw', 'Alex Kendrick', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 5),
(306, 'Your Fault', 'Culpa Tuya, Culpa Tuya – Deine Schuld', '2024', 0.00, 'The love between Noah and Nick seems unbreakable, despite the manoeuvres of their parents to break them up. But his job and her entry into college open their lives to new relationships. The appearance of a revenge-seeking ex-girlfriend and Nick’s mother with unclear intentions will shake the foundations not only of their relationship, but of the Leister family itself. When so many people are out to destroy a love story, can it really end well?', 489, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6kYDG8Imfhph2duBYZeYksHgx7L.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/iQslVnGFJWQzz5kGTvOhU85656f.jpg', NULL, 'Domingo González', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(307, '15 Cameras', '۱۵ دوربین', '2023', 3.06, 'A couple buys a house from The Slumlord Tapes, infamous for hidden cameras and a psycho landlord. It\'s not as safe as they tell themselves.', 457, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/muQrASlFPg4Hx0BEDwXjUsBMSHM.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/yRqfdiRAEPcInhbXpogpYPDY1bp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dHgt3TnswH8', 'Danny Madden', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 4),
(308, 'Twilight', 'Crepusculo 1, La saga Crepúsculo: Crepúsculo, The Twilight Saga 1: Twilight, Twilight sága 1: Stmívání, 暮色', '2008', 3.15, 'When Bella Swan moves to a small town in the Pacific Northwest, she falls in love with Edward Cullen, a mysterious classmate who reveals himself to be a 108-year-old vampire. Despite Edward\'s repeated cautions, Bella can\'t stay away from him, a fatal move that endangers her own life.', 835, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3Gkb6jm6962ADUPaCBqzz9CTbn9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/7eK8FJr4fqq3J5W2xvlr2GVaep2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uxjNDE2fMjI', 'Catherine Hardwicke', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 1),
(309, 'The Last Breath', 'O Último Suspiro', '2024', 3.25, 'A group of old college friends reunite on a Caribbean scuba diving trip exploring the wreckage of a WWII battleship and find themselves trapped inside the underwater labyrinth of rusted metal surrounded by great white sharks.', 921, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vWb8fEIsqKpO36Y7K5QH4DyV7zn.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/pdlQsDrBYJiLSseJNhifC5yhBgF.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVjysY9-L-I', 'Joachim Hedén', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 7),
(310, 'Alien Resurrection', 'Alien 4, Alien 4: Resurrection, 异形：复活, 異形4：浴火重生', '1997', 3.08, 'Two hundred years after Lt. Ripley died, a group of scientists clone her, hoping to breed the ultimate weapon. But the new Ripley is full of surprises … as are the new aliens. Ripley must team with a band of smugglers to keep the creatures from reaching Earth.', 748, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9aRDMlU5Zwpysilm0WCWzU2PCFv.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/f0dFcDXdF6CGz1P1rDzOhwD9hs8.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vu1tVYGsJ1Q', 'Jean-Pierre Jeunet', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 2),
(311, 'The Forbidden Play', 'El último conjuro, Juego prohibido, Kinjirareta asobi', '2023', 2.79, 'Naoto Ihara lives happily with his wife Miyuki and their son Haruto. Their happiness is crushed when Miyuki suddenly dies in a car accident. Naoto falls into deep grief over the death of his wife. Meanwhile, Haruto buries his dead mother Miyuki\'s finger in their garden and prays everyday for her to come back to life. The family is visited by video director Hiroko Kurasawa, who used to work with Naoto Ihara. There she sees Haruto shouting a strange spell in their yard. Unexpected and bizarre phenomenons soon take place around Hiroko Kurasawa.', 709, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t7HSAMstS3S83oMp31vVGHS7cqa.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/cLv78dGV5HcoVgElAI8T4yUPPZX.jpg', NULL, 'Hideo Nakata', '2024-09-08 12:37:21', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 8);
