(352, 'La figliastra - Storia di corna e di passioni', '', '1976', 2.25, 'A long time ago in Sicilia, there was a common, unwritten law that linked the hereditary rights to unequivocal demonstrations of virility. Because of that traditional law, a middle-age widower whose wife died without begetting him a child, is about to lose an inheritance of a large sum of money. The man marries again, with Nadia, an attractive woman with a daughter from her first marriage, Daniela. But time passes, and Nadia is not getting pregnant, either. Eventually, his beautiful stepdaughter will help him solve his problem.', 919, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nsP3QEYN5nswpPwgdNWhqLTHLWz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/gJEDFzztJ9KEs2LZSoKjDbGFgR4.jpg', NULL, 'Edoardo Mulargia', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 9),
(353, 'Resident Evil: Welcome to Raccoon City', 'A kaptár - Raccoon City visszavár, Resident Evil: Καλώς ήλθατε στην Raccoon City, Vùng Đất Quỷ Dữ: Quỷ Dữ Trỗi Dậy, Обитель зла: Раккун Сити, ผีชีวะ: ปฐมบทแห่งเมืองผีดิบ', '2021', 2.99, 'Once the booming home of pharmaceutical giant Umbrella Corporation, Raccoon City is now a dying Midwestern town. The company’s exodus left the city a wasteland…with great evil brewing below the surface. When that evil is unleashed, the townspeople are forever…changed…and a small group of survivors must work together to uncover the truth behind Umbrella and make it through the night.', 519, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bArhvjRHl535XMaSh9VjInF2mSZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/o76ZDm8PS9791XiuieNB93UZcRV.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4q6UGCyHZCI', 'Johannes Roberts', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 1),
(354, 'Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse', 'Animated Spider-Man, Spider Man : nouvelle génération, ספיידרמן: מימד העכביש, سبايدر مان: في عالم العنكبوت', '2018', 4.20, 'Struggling to find his place in the world while juggling school and family, Brooklyn teenager Miles Morales is unexpectedly bitten by a radioactive spider and develops unfathomable powers just like the one and only Spider-Man. While wrestling with the implications of his new abilities, Miles discovers a super collider created by the madman Wilson \"Kingpin\" Fisk, causing others from across the Spider-Verse to be inadvertently transported to his dimension.', 29019, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iiZZdoQBEYBv6id8su7ImL0oCbD.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/qGQf2OHIkoh89K8XeKQzhxczf96.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tg52up16eq0', 'Bob Persichetti', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 5),
(355, 'The Green Mile', 'Gurîn Mairu, Roheline miil, Stephen King\'s The Green Mile, To prasino mili, 綠里奇蹟', '1999', 4.26, 'A supernatural tale set on death row in a Southern prison, where gentle giant John Coffey possesses the mysterious power to heal people\'s ailments. When the cell block\'s head guard, Paul Edgecomb, recognizes Coffey\'s miraculous gift, he tries desperately to help stave off the condemned man\'s execution.', 110, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8VG8fDNiy50H4FedGwdSVUPoaJe.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/vxJ08SvwomfKbpboCWynC3uqUg4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bg7epsq0OIQ', 'Frank Darabont', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 6),
(356, 'Titane', 'Titanium, Titāns, 變鈦, 티탄', '2021', 3.20, 'A woman with a metal plate in her head from a childhood car accident embarks on a bizarre journey, bringing her into contact with a firefighter who\'s reunited with his missing son after 10 years.', 44579, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wcFYmD2GfGBkawNgksv9iFiJPGr.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zEddiBK6yZNUGVnmBJzmnYcEWiR.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_DmFHh7KsWc', 'Julia Ducournau', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 5),
(357, 'The Little Mermaid', 'A Pequena Sereia, De Kleine Zeemeermin, La Petite Sirène, La Sirenetta 1, Litla hafmeyjan', '2023', 3.68, 'This colorful adventure tells the story of an impetuous mermaid princess named Ariel who falls in love with the very human Prince Eric and puts everything on the line for the chance to be with him. Memorable songs and characters -- including the villainous sea witch Ursula.', 562, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8qddUnMT7CgIISEpZi7VCAwDiei.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/qGZXYHvWR1TYOU9raCaEABrj9m7.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kpGo2_d3oYE', 'John Musker', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 8),
(358, 'Apocalypto', 'Apocalypto, Mel Gibson\'s Apocalypto, Đế Chế Maya, Апокаліпто', '2006', 3.79, 'Set in the Mayan civilization, when a man\'s idyllic presence is brutally disrupted by a violent invading force, he is taken on a perilous journey to a world ruled by fear and oppression where a harrowing end awaits him. Through a twist of fate and spurred by the power of his love for his woman and his family he will make a desperate break to return home and to ultimately save his way of life.', 562, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cRY25Q32kDNPFDkFkxAs6bgCq3L.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/hMl124Go2Ed9Qu8VsPLiA3nBSMk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ngWBddVNVZs', 'Mel Gibson', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 2),
(359, 'Detective Conan: Black Iron Submarine', 'Detective Conan The Movie: Black Iron Submarine, Meitantei Conan: Kurogane no Submarine, ยอดนักสืบจิ๋วโคนัน เดอะมูฟวี่ 26: มฤตยูใต้น้ำทมิฬ, 名偵探柯南：黑鐵的魚影', '2023', 3.42, 'Many engineers from around the world gather at the Interpol marine facility \"Pacific Buoy\" on Hachijo-jima, in the sea south of central Tokyo Prefecture coast, to witness the launch of a new system that connects all law enforcement camera systems around the world and enables facial recognition worldwide. Conan, along with his friends Kogoro, Ran, Agasa, Haibara, and the Detective Boys, also heads to the island with an invitation from Sonoko to see the whales. He receives a message from Subaru, who says that a Europol agent has been murdered in Germany by Gin. Perturbed, Conan sneaks onto the police ship led by Kuroda, which is bringing them to the island to protect the completion work, and tours the new facility, just in time for the Black Organization to kidnap a female engineer, seeking a piece of important data in her USB drive. A terrifying howl of screws is heard from the ocean as an unknown person approaches Haibara.', 631, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gLaJOggH5fP0DyeI7Jkpr78B0lc.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/uKTkiw3w3LfdzgiPOvu0C19Voi3.jpg', NULL, 'Yuzuru Tachikawa', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 7),
(360, 'Cabrini', 'Una mujer italiana', '2024', 3.70, 'Italian immigrant Francesca Cabrini arrives in 1889 New York City and is greeted by disease, crime, and impoverished children. Cabrini sets off on a daring mission to convince the hostile mayor to secure housing and healthcare for society\'s most vulnerable. With broken English and poor health, Cabrini uses her entrepreneurial mind to build an empire of hope unlike anything the world had ever seen.', 465, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rBiHiN8W4BqMFrDozemzkof7GmF.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jwmswCW3U8Uh0wEo46psJpgXejD.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZaMlUazXvyY', 'Alejandro Monteverde', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(361, 'Turning Red', 'Devenir rouge, Es sarkstu, เขินแรงแดงเป็นแพนด้า, 变红, 터닝 레드', '2022', 3.70, 'Thirteen-year-old Mei is experiencing the awkwardness of being a teenager with a twist – when she gets too excited, she transforms into a giant red panda.', 41539, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qsdjk9oAKSQMWs0Vt5Pyfh6O4GZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/fOy2Jurz9k6RnJnMUMRDAgBwru2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XdKzUbAiswE', 'Domee Shi', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 3),
(362, 'Terminator 2: Judgment Day', 'T2, Terminaator 2: Kohtupäev, Terminator 2 - Il giorno del giudizio - Director\'s Cut, Terminator 2: Judgement Day, 未來戰士續集', '1991', 4.06, 'Set ten years after the events of the original, James Cameron’s classic sci-fi action flick tells the story of a second attempt to get the rid of rebellion leader John Connor, this time targeting the boy himself. However, the rebellion has sent a reprogrammed terminator to protect Connor.', 868, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5M0j0B18abtBI5gi2RhfjjurTqb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/vINgGecnz95iDL6fjQMARDsocgG.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DX1Y8e7i6cw', 'James Cameron', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 1),
(363, 'The Suicide Squad', 'Az Öngyilkos Osztag, L\'Escadron Suicide : La Mission, Suicide Squad 2, Отрядът самоубийци, ザ・スーサイド・スクワッド', '2021', 3.75, 'Supervillains Harley Quinn, Bloodsport, Peacemaker and a collection of nutty cons at Belle Reve prison join the super-secret, super-shady Task Force X as they are dropped off at the remote, enemy-infused island of Corto Maltese.', 963, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kb4s0ML0iVZlG6wAKbbs9NAm6X.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jlGmlFOcfo8n5tURmhC7YVd4Iyy.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eg5ciqQzmK0', 'James Gunn', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 8),
(364, 'The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey', 'A Hobbit: Egy váratlan utazás, Hobbiten: En uventet reise, O Hobbit - Uma Jornada Inesperada, The Hobbit - An Unexpected Journey - 3D', '2012', 3.70, 'Bilbo Baggins, a hobbit enjoying his quiet life, is swept into an epic quest by Gandalf the Grey and thirteen dwarves who seek to reclaim their mountain home from Smaug, the dragon.', 24096, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yHA9Fc37VmpUA5UncTxxo3rTGVA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/xyXmtuvsoM5J3yNad0nvcetpBdY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXqZK-nbZ74', 'Peter Jackson', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 8),
(365, 'Howl\'s Moving Castle', 'Haulov pokretni zamak, Hauru no Ugoku Shiro, Замок-мандрівник, Подвижният замък на Хол, Шагающий замок Хаула', '2004', 4.20, 'Sophie, a young milliner, is turned into an elderly woman by a witch who enters her shop and curses her. She encounters a wizard named Howl and gets caught up in his resistance to fighting for the king.', 921, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6pZgH10jhpToPcf0uvyTCPFhWpI.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/xqaN2WYQclQlqvKvsOcNgOx2vRn.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2x5SejvTMeA', 'Hayao Miyazaki', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 3),
(366, 'Delinquent in Drag', 'La canaglia in minigonna, Oira sukeban', '1992', 2.10, 'Does being the only guy in an all girl school sound like paradise? It might be, if the girls knew you were a guy, but to stay in school teenage pervert Banji can\'t let can\'t let anyone find out his chromosomes don\'t match. Banji\'s status conscious parents want him to go to a good school, but not enough to spend the money on a good co-ed school. Now, in addition to studying math and science, Banji has to learn how to put on a bra and makeup. His life has become a living hell. Not only is he at the bottom of the social pecking order, he must also got to conceal his inner-masculinity from the pretty classmate girl who\'s stolen his heart while avoiding the female bullies who threaten to expose his less-than-feminine charms in the locker room.', 354, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rWEykM1thLhYee6mK25fGLXyO14.jpg', 'N/A', NULL, 'Yusaku Saotome', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 6),
(367, 'Kraven the Hunter', 'كرايفن ذي هانتر', '2024', 0.00, 'Sergei Kravinoff is a big game hunter, who takes a magical serum giving him superhuman abilities and a longer life.', 484, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/i47IUSsN126K11JUzqQIOi1Mg1M.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/v9Du2HC3hlknAvGlWhquRbeifwW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hR1-ihzff3I', 'J.C. Chandor', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(368, 'White Chicks', 'As Branquelas, Dos Rubias De Pelo En Pecho, Loiras à Força, ¿Y dónde están las rubias?, בחורות לבנות', '2004', 3.48, 'Two FBI agent brothers, Marcus and Kevin Copeland, accidentally foil a drug bust. To avoid being fired they accept a mission escorting a pair of socialites to the Hamptons--but when the girls are disfigured in a car accident, they refuse to go. Left without options, Marcus and Kevin decide to pose as the sisters, transforming themselves from black men into rich white women.', 94, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aHTUpo45qy9QYIOnVITGGqLoVcA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/di47xqYMCYpjqwnqNlO17X5qXMX.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aeVkbNka9HM', 'Keenen Ivory Wayans', '2024-09-08 12:37:22', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 9),
(369, 'Hidden Desire', 'Hidden Desire, Ngoh wai hing kong', '1991', 2.34, 'David is sitting in a bar, musing over why he has bedded and left five or six of Asia\'s loveliest women in such a short time.', 90943, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/39cD7X07Nrt3wsEqcYP1n9BhjX2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/spJ063LkpTk2BMiYx4L1dOGZnBv.jpg', NULL, 'Ho Fan', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(370, 'Princess Mononoke', 'A Princesa Mononoke, Mononoke Hime, Princesa Mononoke, Princeza Mononoke, 원령공주', '1997', 4.17, 'Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.', 139, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/gl0jzn4BupSbL2qMVeqrjKkF9Js.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=opCxPAwdB6U', 'Hayao Miyazaki', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 5),
(371, 'Inception', 'El Origen, 인셉션', '2010', 4.19, 'Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible: \"inception\", the implantation of another person\'s idea into a target\'s subconscious.', 956, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ljsZTbVsrQSqZgWeep2B1QiDKuh.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/8ZTVqvKDQ8emSGUEMjsS4yHAwrp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cdx31ak4KbQ', 'Christopher Nolan', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 10),
(372, 'After the Pandemic', 'پس از همه‌گیری جهانی, 全境灾变', '2022', 2.48, 'Set in a post-apocalyptic world where a global airborne pandemic has wiped out 90% of the Earth\'s population and only the young and immune have endured as scavengers. For Ellie and Quinn, the daily challenges to stay alive are compounded when they become hunted by the merciless Stalkers.', 503, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p1LbrdJ53dGfEhRopG71akfzOVu.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/9c0lHTXRqDBxeOToVzRu0GArSne.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UZCVv3SFNtE', 'Richard Lowry', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 1),
(373, 'Jennifer\'s Body', 'Dzeniferes kunas, El cuerpo de Jennifer, Tijelo lijepe Jennifer, Zabójcze cialo, 辣得要命', '2009', 2.98, 'Jennifer, a gorgeous, seductive cheerleader takes evil to a whole new level after she\'s possessed by a sinister demon. Now it\'s up to her best friend to stop Jennifer\'s reign of terror before it\'s too late.', 93765, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wrkjsGcFJxcQqR56kJUYAEKKg2T.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/dcqbt5j5K6oMnz2kdEpJY8iG20i.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8azftM5puI', 'Karyn Kusama', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 2),
(374, 'The Goat Life', 'Aadu Jeevitham, 山羊生活', '2024', 3.93, 'Indian migrant worker Najeeb Muhammad goes to Saudi Arabia to earn money. However, in a twist of fate, he finds himself living a slave-like existence, herding goats in the middle of the desert.', 974, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vwRkVhvJuAFz4i8udXMNkcJCztc.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/u7GXKY7EUTBS4kQO6aXqDNXWgpd.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qvsiJKdDxPs', 'Blessy', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 5),
(375, 'Bad Boys for Life', 'Bad Boys 3, Bad Boys 3, Bad Boys Para Siempre, Băieţi răi 3, Dos Policías Rebeldes Por Siempre, Плохие парни 3', '2020', 3.57, 'Marcus and Mike are forced to confront new threats, career changes, and midlife crises as they join the newly created elite team AMMO of the Miami police department to take down the ruthless Armando Armas, the vicious leader of a Miami drug cartel.', 80, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/y95lQLnuNKdPAzw9F9Ab8kJ80c3.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/3N316jUSdhvPyYTW29G4v9ebbcS.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R228yPrwqTo', 'Bilall Fallah', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 4),
(376, 'Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings', 'Shang Chi y la leyenda de los diez anillos, Shang-Chi at ang Alamat ng Sampung Singsing, Шанґ Чі та Легенда Десяти Кілець, شانج شي وأسطورة الخواتم العشرة, شانغ-چي وأسطورة الحلقات العشر', '2021', 3.78, 'Shang-Chi must confront the past he thought he left behind when he is drawn into the web of the mysterious Ten Rings organization.', 74542, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9f2Q0U3IOsLgrI2HkvldwSABZy5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/rAksPS6LjBONzY84szQBz5gGej6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8YjFbMbfXaQ', 'Destin Daniel Cretton', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 7),
(377, 'Finding Nemo', 'Finding Nemo 3D, Hitta Nemo 3D, Op zoek naar Nemo, نيمو', '2003', 3.91, 'Nemo, an adventurous young clownfish, is unexpectedly taken from his Great Barrier Reef home to a dentist\'s office aquarium. It\'s up to his worrisome father Marlin and a friendly but forgetful fish Dory to bring Nemo home -- meeting vegetarian sharks, surfer dude turtles, hypnotic jellyfish, hungry seagulls, and more along the way.', 53623, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eHuGQ10FUzK1mdOY69wF5pGgEf5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/eCynaAOgYYiw5yN5lBwz3IxqvaW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZS_8btMjx2U', 'Andrew Stanton', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 2),
(378, 'The Terminator', 'El exteminador, Tamineta, Terminaattori, Terminator: El exterminador', '1984', 3.83, 'In the post-apocalyptic future, reigning tyrannical supercomputers teleport a cyborg assassin known as the \"Terminator\" back to 1984 to kill Sarah Connor, whose unborn son is destined to lead insurgents against 21st century mechanical hegemony. Meanwhile, the human-resistance movement dispatches a lone warrior to safeguard Sarah. Can he stop the virtually indestructible killing machine?', 598, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qvktm0BHcnmDpul4Hz01GIazWPr.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/ffdqHMWkh1h9MABwIfbfRJhgFW6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nGrW-OR2uDk', 'James Cameron', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(379, '20th Century Girl', '20世紀のキミ：2022, 20세기 소녀', '2022', 4.08, 'In 1999, a teen girl keeps close tabs on a boy in school on behalf of her deeply smitten best friend – then she gets swept up in a love story of her own.', 94032, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/od22ftNnyag0TTxcnJhlsu3aLoU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/37y53Jt8K6MvN6s4zJVFa61luO2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFS4_qevE7M', 'Bang Woo-ri', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 2),
(380, 'Ice Age', 'I epochí ton pagetónon, Ice Age - jäätikön sankarit, Ledeno doba, Lednikovyj period, Lʹodovykovyy period', '2002', 3.68, 'With the impending ice age almost upon them, a mismatched trio of prehistoric critters – Manny the woolly mammoth, Diego the saber-toothed tiger and Sid the giant sloth – find an orphaned infant and decide to return it to its human parents. Along the way, the unlikely allies become friends but, when enemies attack, their quest takes on far nobler aims.', 474, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gLhHHZUzeseRXShoDyC4VqLgsNv.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/kK5OeulwVDniPgjNOGHvzcORzdG.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tqdcLzM3ciQ', 'Chris Wedge', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 1),
(381, 'Ice Age', 'I epochí ton pagetónon, Ice Age - jäätikön sankarit, Ledeno doba, Lednikovyj period, Lʹodovykovyy period', '2002', 3.68, 'With the impending ice age almost upon them, a mismatched trio of prehistoric critters – Manny the woolly mammoth, Diego the saber-toothed tiger and Sid the giant sloth – find an orphaned infant and decide to return it to its human parents. Along the way, the unlikely allies become friends but, when enemies attack, their quest takes on far nobler aims.', 573, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gLhHHZUzeseRXShoDyC4VqLgsNv.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/kK5OeulwVDniPgjNOGHvzcORzdG.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tqdcLzM3ciQ', 'Chris Wedge', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 5),
(382, 'The Bikeriders', 'El Club de los Vándalos, Les Motards, Байкери, 摩托黑帮, 더 바이크라이더스', '2024', 3.45, 'After a chance encounter, headstrong Kathy is drawn to Benny, member of Midwestern motorcycle club the Vandals. As the club transforms into a dangerous underworld of violence, Benny must choose between Kathy and his loyalty to the club.', 997, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qTb6sSRt8Pw96JTan8ezU2xO0FU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/kwGvFyRtGSSm8AFfnRNXoZTQmJj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7W0ec8UMnfg', 'Jeff Nichols', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(383, 'Boy Kills World', 'Boy vs le monde, Contra Todos, Dečko ubija svijet, Oğlan hamıya qarşı, بوی دنیا را نابود می‌کند', '2024', 3.43, 'When his family is murdered, a deaf-mute named Boy escapes to the jungle and is trained by a mysterious shaman to repress his childish imagination and become an instrument of death.', 613, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/25JskXmchcYwj3jHRmcPm738MpB.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/1m1rXopfNDVL3UMiv6kriYaJ3yE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z6NibtjmjOk', 'Moritz Mohr', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(384, 'Hotel Transylvania: Transformania', 'Hotel Transylvania 4, Hôtel Transylvanie 4, Готель Трансільванія: Трансформанія, Монстры на каникулах 4, 몬스터 호텔 4: 뒤바뀐 세계', '2022', 3.54, 'When Van Helsing\'s mysterious invention, the \"Monsterfication Ray,\" goes haywire, Drac and his monster pals are all transformed into humans, and Johnny becomes a monster. In their new mismatched bodies, Drac and Johnny must team up and race across the globe to find a cure before it\'s too late, and before they drive each other crazy.', 521, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/teCy1egGQa0y8ULJvlrDHQKnxBL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/ep1urICLqtwwV1sTPHP9WXV4Uto.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6suJohjIvfo', 'Derek Drymon', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 6),
(385, 'Orion and the Dark', 'La Nuit d\'Orion, Orion e o Escuro, Orión y la oscuridad, Арыён і цемра', '2024', 3.30, 'A boy with an active imagination faces his fears on an unforgettable journey through the night with his new friend: a giant, smiling creature named Dark.', 908, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k6iHs4daxm0RQqFQsE8oE5wWJjj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zLj0peaxy5y2SlC6wNIQ4V0pfqg.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cEU3tnJrouE', 'Sean Charmatz', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 3);
