(386, 'Spider-Man: Far From Home', 'Người Nhện  Xa Nhà, Spider-Man - Far from Home, Spider-Man 2: Far from Home, 스파이더맨-파 프롬 홈', '2019', 3.72, 'Peter Parker and his friends go on a summer trip to Europe. However, they will hardly be able to rest - Peter will have to agree to help Nick Fury uncover the mystery of creatures that cause natural disasters and destruction throughout the continent.', 189, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4q2NNj4S5dG2RLF9CpXsej7yXl.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/34jW8LvjRplM8Pv06cBFDpLlenR.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LFoz8ZJWmPs', 'Jon Watts', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 8),
(387, 'The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds & Snakes', 'Die Tribute von Panem - Das Lied von Vogel und Schlange, Hunger Games 0, The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds and Snakes, Đấu Trường Sinh Tử: Khúc Ca Của Chim Ca & Rắn Độc, عطش مبارزه: تصنیف پرندگان آوازخوان و مارها', '2023', 3.55, '64 years before he becomes the tyrannical president of Panem, Coriolanus Snow sees a chance for a change in fortunes when he mentors Lucy Gray Baird, the female tribute from District 12.', 802, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mBaXZ95R2OxueZhvQbcEWy2DqyO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/8GnWDLn2AhnmkQ7hlQ9NJUYobSS.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NxW_X4kzeus', 'Francis Lawrence', '2024-09-08 12:37:23', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 9),
(388, 'Sri Asih', 'Alana - Déesse de justice, Sri Asih, スリ・アシィ, 스리 아시', '2022', 3.10, 'Alana discover the truth about her origin: she’s not an ordinary human being. She may be the gift for humanity and become its protector as Sri Asih. Or a destruction, if she can’t control her anger.', 378, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wShcJSKMFg1Dy1yq7kEZuay6pLS.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/oFAukXiMPrwLpbulGmB5suEZlrm.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QeT6Ke2kQYo', 'Upi Avianto', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 8),
(389, 'The Greatest of All Time', 'GOAT, Thalapathy 68', '2024', 2.25, 'A once decorated member of the Special Anti-Terrorism Squad (SATS) is called back into action by his former colleagues for an important mission, setting him on a dangerous collision course with his own past.', 63, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oyyu7F4yq26tgNutX4zNEiliV1O.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/weAaHO7lpQPDU0Wn15wQWBIzA61.jpg', NULL, 'Venkat Prabhu', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 1),
(390, 'Schindler\'s List', 'Lista Shindlera, قائمة شندلر, シンドラーのリスト, 舒特拉的名單', '1993', 4.29, 'The true story of how businessman Oskar Schindler saved over a thousand Jewish lives from the Nazis while they worked as slaves in his factory during World War II.', 829, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sF1U4EUQS8YHUYjNl3pMGNIQyr0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zb6fM1CX41D9rF9hdgclu0peUmy.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mxphAlJID9U', 'Steven Spielberg', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 10),
(391, 'Star Wars', 'Guerre stellari (Episodio IV), Star Wars: Episod IV – Nytt hopp, Star Wars: Episode IV – A New Hope, Star Wars: Una Nueva Esperanza, 스타 워즈 에피소드 4: 새로운 희망', '1977', 4.10, 'Princess Leia is captured and held hostage by the evil Imperial forces in their effort to take over the galactic Empire. Venturesome Luke Skywalker and dashing captain Han Solo team together with the loveable robot duo R2-D2 and C-3PO to rescue the beautiful princess and restore peace and justice in the Empire.', 706, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6FfCtAuVAW8XJjZ7eWeLibRLWTw.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jNjT5y95BToczcxgVPl1NBB7goY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XsS1yE2f-hE', 'George Lucas', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 9),
(392, 'Sting', 'Sting: Araña Asesina, لدغة, گزش, 屋中异蛛, 屋中異蛛', '2024', 3.15, 'After raising an unnervingly talented spider in secret, 12-year-old Charlotte must face the truth about her pet and fight for her family\'s survival.', 701, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zuSAZIG1PSrxFwPeAlGtg9LTwxo.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/k37Ccgu05Am1xxgN5GaW0HX9Kkl.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cPHQxTVXMM', 'Kiah Roache-Turner', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 6),
(393, 'Sing 2', 'Cantar! 2, 星夢動物園 2, 欢乐好声音2, 歡樂好聲音2, 씽 2', '2021', 3.94, 'Buster and his new cast now have their sights set on debuting a new show at the Crystal Tower Theater in glamorous Redshore City. But with no connections, he and his singers must sneak into the Crystal Entertainment offices, run by the ruthless wolf mogul Jimmy Crystal, where the gang pitches the ridiculous idea of casting the lion rock legend Clay Calloway in their show. Buster must embark on a quest to find the now-isolated Clay and persuade him to return to the stage.', 210, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aWeKITRFbbwY8txG5uCj4rMCfSP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/6mJrgL7Mi13XjJeGYJFlD6UEVQw.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EPZu5MA2uqI', 'Garth Jennings', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 10),
(394, 'Mean Girls', 'Kötü Kızlar, Mean Girls: The Musical, Meninas Malvadas: O Musical', '2024', 3.00, 'New student Cady Heron is welcomed into the top of the social food chain by the elite group of popular girls called ‘The Plastics,’ ruled by the conniving queen bee Regina George and her minions Gretchen and Karen. However, when Cady makes the major misstep of falling for Regina’s ex-boyfriend Aaron Samuels, she finds herself prey in Regina’s crosshairs. As Cady sets to take down the group’s apex predator with the help of her outcast friends Janis and Damian, she must learn how to stay true to herself while navigating the most cutthroat jungle of all: high school.', 87629, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fbbj3viSUDEGT1fFFMNpHP1iUjw.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/accTIUygtg24TM7wT7uQMMdvYUW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qs6Ne-Bqn6U', 'Arturo Perez Jr.', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 4),
(395, 'GoodFellas', 'Buenos Muchachos, Sıkı Dostlar, Τα καλά παιδιά', '1990', 4.23, 'The true story of Henry Hill, a half-Irish, half-Sicilian Brooklyn kid who is adopted by neighbourhood gangsters at an early age and climbs the ranks of a Mafia family under the guidance of Jimmy Conway.', 875, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aKuFiU82s5ISJpGZp7YkIr3kCUd.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/7TF4p86ZafnxFuNqWdhpHXFO244.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PTBRNXGQR9Q', 'Martin Scorsese', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 5),
(396, 'Golden Kamuy', 'Golden Kamuy, 黄金神威 真人电影版', '2024', 3.32, 'On the Hokkaido frontier, a war veteran and Ainu girl race against misfits and military renegades to find treasure mapped out on tattooed outlaws.', 654, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sLcRGIJqlJeoGGk88CtA8Ida5aq.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jaRoloTuVFYYvBH5VlRBQnf2egx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N6DmjhcSt8Q', 'Shigeaki Kubo', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 1),
(397, 'Through My Window 3: Looking at You', 'À travers ma fenêtre 3 - Les yeux dans les yeux, Dalla mia finestra: Guardando te, Gjennom vinduet mitt 3: Jeg ser deg, Qua ô cửa sổ 3: Ta nhìn thấy nhau, Through My Window: Looking at You', '2024', 3.48, 'After the events of the summer, Ares and Raquel they don\'t see a way forward in their relationship and decide to go separate ways. But when they meet again in the winter in Barcelona, the love and desire they feel for each other is undeniable. Will they be able to find a way to get back together?', 76154, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gwpTgtwVAwmvivBN8rAQABpx9Am.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zhoR3SwYxXyKzGwbz4DBgkyeFfv.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G_WsQNsfx1Q', 'Marçal Forés', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 8),
(398, 'Flipped', 'Flipped - Il primo amore non si scorda mai, 萌动青春', '2010', 4.01, 'When Juli meets Bryce in the second grade, she knows it\'s true love. After spending six years trying to convince Bryce the same, she\'s ready to give up - until he starts to reconsider.', 423, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6zDYFigohwncqFL00MKbFV01dWb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/xBSwwkAYl9h8QVG2OxNpSaSgJwr.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aXeJ8NM7c9g', 'Rob Reiner', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 5),
(399, 'Alien³', 'Alien³: Special \'Assembly Cut\' Edition, Чужий 3, Чужой 3, 에일리언 3', '1992', 3.19, 'After escaping with Newt and Hicks from the alien planet, Ripley crash lands on Fiorina 161, a prison planet and host to a correctional facility. Unfortunately, although Newt and Hicks do not survive the crash, a more unwelcome visitor does. The prison does not allow weapons of any kind, and with aid being a long time away, the prisoners must simply survive in any way they can.', 794, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xh5wI0UoW7DfS1IyLy3d2CgrCEP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/nEmOmbCWBXS3tHU2N49z693KDK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e45rAwndek8', 'David Fincher', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 9),
(400, 'Freelance', 'Na volné noze, روزنامه‌نگار آزاد, จ็อบระห่ำ คนถึกระทึกโลก', '2023', 3.25, 'An ex-special forces operative takes a job to provide security for a journalist as she interviews a dictator, but a military coup breaks out in the middle of the interview, they are forced to escape into the jungle where they must survive.', 59333, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7Bd4EUOqQDKZXA6Od5gkfzRNb0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zIYROrkHJPYB3VTiW1L9QVgaQO.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0k2XerT8Nw', 'Pierre Morel', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 2),
(401, 'Freelance', 'Na volné noze, روزنامه‌نگار آزاد, จ็อบระห่ำ คนถึกระทึกโลก', '2023', 3.25, 'An ex-special forces operative takes a job to provide security for a journalist as she interviews a dictator, but a military coup breaks out in the middle of the interview, they are forced to escape into the jungle where they must survive.', 868, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7Bd4EUOqQDKZXA6Od5gkfzRNb0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zIYROrkHJPYB3VTiW1L9QVgaQO.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0k2XerT8Nw', 'Pierre Morel', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 6),
(402, 'Shrek the Third', 'Shrek 3, Shrek 3 - De Derde, Shrek 3 - The Third, 史力加3', '2007', 3.15, 'The King of Far Far Away has died and Shrek and Fiona are to become King & Queen. However, Shrek wants to return to his cozy swamp and live in peace and quiet, so when he finds out there is another heir to the throne, they set off to bring him back to rule the kingdom.', 93, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n4SexGGQzI26E269tfpa80MZaGV.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/qSNz1G1Ts8fFw6v4Vae4aMAjcY7.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_MoIr7811Bs', 'Chris Miller', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 2),
(403, 'The Godfather Part II', 'El Padrino II, Kummisetä, osa II, Le Parrain 2, The Godfather Part 2', '1974', 4.29, 'In the continuing saga of the Corleone crime family, a young Vito Corleone grows up in Sicily and in 1910s New York. In the 1950s, Michael Corleone attempts to expand the family business into Las Vegas, Hollywood and Cuba.', 144, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hek3koDUyRQk7FIhPXsa6mT2Zc3.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/kGzFbGhp99zva6oZODW5atUtnqi.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7pfqivkYUlE', 'Francis Ford Coppola', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 3),
(404, 'The Hangover', 'Hangover Part 1, Másnaposak, Pohmakas, Se Beber, Não Case, The Hangover: Theatrical Version', '2009', 3.66, 'When three friends finally come to after a raucous night of bachelor-party revelry, they find a baby in the closet and a tiger in the bathroom. But they can\'t seem to locate their best friend, Doug – who\'s supposed to be tying the knot. Launching a frantic search for Doug, the trio perseveres through a nasty hangover to try to make it to the church on time.', 76940, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uluhlXubGu1VxU63X9VHCLWDAYP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/sV49hOlUky6AhVYl4K0d3rergTA.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tlize92ffnY', 'Todd Phillips', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(405, 'xXx: Return of Xander Cage', 'Xander Returns, XXX: Hiloukh gavoha', '2017', 3.07, 'Xander Cage is left for dead after an incident, though he secretly returns to action for a new, tough assignment with his handler Augustus Gibbons.', 98036, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hba8zREJpP1AYhaXgb2oJLQeO0K.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/4QLdZ2A8mkDWp2rpfgDrwmeCtUW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ziu6JzJTZ0', 'D. J. Caruso', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 6),
(406, 'Thor: Love and Thunder', 'Thor 4, Тор 4, থর: প্রেম এবং বজ্রপাত, 雷神4：爱与雷霆', '2022', 3.23, 'After his retirement is interrupted by Gorr the God Butcher, a galactic killer who seeks the extinction of the gods, Thor Odinson enlists the help of King Valkyrie, Korg, and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster, who now wields Mjolnir as the Mighty Thor. Together they embark upon a harrowing cosmic adventure to uncover the mystery of the God Butcher’s vengeance and stop him before it’s too late.', 806, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pIkRyD18kl4FhoCNQuWxWu5cBLM.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jsoz1HlxczSuTx0mDl2h0lxy36l.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Go8nTmfrQd8', 'Taika Waititi', '2024-09-08 12:37:24', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 4),
