(436, 'Fight Club', 'Boen klub, Borilački klub, Boytsovskiy klub, Kláb máchis, Mo\'adon Krav', '1999', 4.22, 'A ticking-time-bomb insomniac and a slippery soap salesman channel primal male aggression into a shocking new form of therapy. Their concept catches on, with underground \"fight clubs\" forming in every town, until an eccentric gets in the way and ignites an out-of-control spiral toward oblivion.', 95, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pB8BM7pdSp6B6Ih7QZ4DrQ3PmJK.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/hZkgoQYus5vegHoetLkCJzb17zJ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dfeUzm6KF4g', 'David Fincher', '2024-09-08 12:37:25', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 9),
(437, 'Woody Woodpecker Goes to Camp', 'El Pájaro Loco ¡Lío en el campamento!, Pica-Pau: Acampamento de Férias, Woody Woodpecker 2', '2024', 3.26, 'After getting kicked out of the forest, Woody thinks he\'s found a forever home at Camp Woo Hoo — until an inspector threatens to shut down the camp.', 922, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6hw6zvAsBSMyDxnk68XPpjZZyvz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/cIztAxDn3H8JylRaJwiHHpkGe53.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZYjbfLQDYvg', 'Jonathan A. Rosenbaum', '2024-09-08 12:37:25', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 7),
(438, 'Spider-Man', 'Lyudyna-pavuk, Spaĭdŭr-men, Spajdermen, Spider-Man: The Motion Picture', '2002', 3.65, 'After being bitten by a genetically altered spider at Oscorp, nerdy but endearing high school student Peter Parker is endowed with amazing powers to become the superhero known as Spider-Man.', 72449, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gh4cZbhZxyTbgxQPxD0dOudNPTn.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/2PDTWfuBWQKVC7aPAqJK5UCpz08.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t06RUxPbp_c', 'Sam Raimi', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 3),
(439, 'The Count of Monte-Cristo', 'O Conde de Monte Cristo', '2002', 4.21, 'Edmond Dantes becomes the target of a sinister plot and is arrested on his wedding day for a crime he did not commit. After 14 years in the island prison of Château d’If, he manages a daring escape. Now rich beyond his dreams, he assumes the identity of the Count of Monte-Cristo and exacts his revenge on the three men who betrayed him.', 154, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aHRUsFln97FlIdsvYKFT3z5ubYE.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/i9qxG4UVgfX4AdMGnfRzMYEowLQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TsQnK5_5VSk', 'Alexandre de La Patellière', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 1),
(440, 'A Family Affair', 'A Family Affair, Οικογενειακό Ζήτημα, مسألة عائلية, เรื่อง (รัก) ในครอบครัว', '2024', 2.96, 'The only thing worse than being the assistant to a high-maintenance movie star who doesn\'t take you seriously? Finding out he\'s smitten with your mom.', 544, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l0CaVyqnTsWwNd4hWsrLNEk1Wjd.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/ngLxW9WqQAkTCBTcjOSt2Pnz5qZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ytc2eifpiuQ', 'Richard LaGravenese', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 4),
(441, 'Cinderella', 'Aschenbrödel, Aschenputtel, Cenicienta, Cinderella I, Zolushka', '2015', 3.53, 'Cinderella has faith her dreams of a better life will come true. With help from her loyal mice friends and a wave of her Fairy Godmother\'s wand, Cinderella\'s rags are magically turned into a glorious gown and off she goes to the Royal Ball. But when the clock strikes midnight, the spell is broken, leaving a single glass slipper... the only key to the ultimate fairy-tale ending!', 23799, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4nssBcQUBadCTBjrAkX46mVEKts.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/rH0DPF7pB35jxLxKb3JRUgCrrnp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n44EWI92Tc8', 'Hamilton Luske', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 9),
(442, 'Spider-Man 3', 'Spider-Man 3: The IMAX Experience, Σπάιντερμαν 3, Людина-павук 3. Ворог у відбитті, 스파이더맨3', '2007', 3.20, 'The seemingly invincible Spider-Man goes up against an all-new crop of villains—including the shape-shifting Sandman. While Spider-Man’s superpowers are altered by an alien organism, his alter ego, Peter Parker, deals with nemesis Eddie Brock and also gets caught up in a love triangle.', 997, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qFmwhVUoUSXjkKRmca5yGDEXBIj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/w1oD1MzHjnBJc5snKupIQaSBLIh.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wPosLpgMtTY', 'Sam Raimi', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 5),
(443, 'Fifty Shades Freed', '50 tons de liberdade, Cinquante Nuances de Grey 3 - Cinquantes Nuances Plus Claires, Femtio nyanser av frihet, Fifty Shades Of Grey 3: Fifty Shades Freed', '2018', 3.36, 'Believing they have left behind shadowy figures from their past, newlyweds Christian and Ana fully embrace an inextricable connection and shared life of luxury. But just as she steps into her role as Mrs. Grey and he relaxes into an unfamiliar stability, new threats could jeopardize their happy ending before it even begins.', 998, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vwFR5WI1RQ1RCxS0cdTbiSgaXJr.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/jjuDhXlAY7yHc50t8gEZWvlkoEn.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nJCc5HRPxYA', 'James Foley', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 3),
(444, 'Nightcrawler', 'Gece Qurdu, Kha\'yat ha\'laila, Naujienų medžiotojas, Str1ng0r, Стерв’ятник', '2014', 3.86, 'When Lou Bloom, desperate for work, muscles into the world of L.A. crime journalism, he blurs the line between observer and participant to become the star of his own story. Aiding him in his effort is Nina, a TV-news veteran.', 26531, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j9HrX8f7GbZQm1BrBiR40uFQZSb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/wofhl2lsTYCPmMQPsbj6iu9n0P6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7uaYhPpV7G4', 'Dan Gilroy', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 3),
(445, 'Justice League: Crisis on Infinite Earths Part Two', 'Liga da Justiça: Crise nas Infinitas Terras - Parte 2, 正义联盟：无限地球危机（中）', '2024', 3.51, 'An endless army of shadow demons bent on the destruction of all reality swarms over our world and all parallel Earths! The only thing opposing them is the mightiest team of metahumans ever assembled. But not even the combined power of Superman, Batman, Wonder Woman, Green Lantern and all their fellow superheroes can slow down the onslaught of this invincible horde. What mysterious force is driving them? And how do the long-buried secrets of the Monitor and Supergirl threaten to crush our last defense?', 381, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/g8ak4QAGLZpqMs3CpnFHWWfIzJQ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/tBmJCH9llj1Q9jDOS7vGWnl7GVj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6jtfmXziNQ', 'Jeff Wamester', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 1),
(446, 'Peter Pan', 'Les Aventures de Peter Pan, Peter Pan 1, Peter Pan: 1, Peter Pans heitere Abenteuer, 피터팬', '2003', 3.61, 'Leaving the safety of their nursery behind, Wendy, Michael and John follow Peter Pan to a magical world where childhood lasts forever. But while in Neverland, the kids must face Captain Hook and foil his attempts to get rid of Peter for good.', 183, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6UTZmeQcxbtW32MyR5nKIx7ID4f.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/vwcfvPzYO3Gz975yRXp6DYSSbzo.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gVC0bENF-Ec', 'Clyde Geronimi', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 4),
(447, 'Fall', 'A Queda, Fall, Kritiens, 命懸二千呎, 坠', '2022', 3.60, 'For best friends Becky and Hunter, life is all about conquering fears and pushing limits. But after they climb 2,000 feet to the top of a remote, abandoned radio tower, they find themselves stranded with no way down. Now Becky and Hunter’s expert climbing skills will be put to the ultimate test as they desperately fight to survive the elements, a lack of supplies, and vertigo-inducing heights', 157, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v28T5F1IygM8vXWZIycfNEm3xcL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/hlxduUs8y9icWGMzYCDLcYHEQ2u.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNk7Cu4sJOs', 'Scott Mann', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 3),
(448, 'Vikings: Battle of Heirs', 'وایکینگ‌ها: نبرد وارثان', '2023', 3.07, 'A young Viking must come to terms with the realization that he may be the King\'s son, who was switched at birth, but not before others try to take his rightful place.', 184, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/87goLbbqrJqAxqDS5cBsik1zKT.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/4Ep2KivIBUZbkS7kHjW7Qywnhhj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PfaJiHP1oHU', 'Robin Keane', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 9),
(449, 'Blue Beetle', 'Blue Beetle: Bọ Hung Xanh, Kék Bogár, Синий Жук, Синия Бръмбар, החיפושית הכחולה', '2023', 3.38, 'Recent college grad Jaime Reyes returns home full of aspirations for his future, only to find that home is not quite as he left it. As he searches to find his purpose in the world, fate intervenes when Jaime unexpectedly finds himself in possession of an ancient relic of alien biotechnology: the Scarab.', 248, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mXLOHHc1Zeuwsl4xYKjKh2280oL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/xzdOIL7261CWehsHOk3lnP0xqam.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4wxyy8Rcz4k', 'Ángel Manuel Soto', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 2),
(450, 'Kingsman: The Secret Service', 'Kingsman - Serviço Secreto, Kingsman - The Secret Service, 皇家特工：間諜密令, 金牌特务, 킹스맨: 시크릿 에이전트', '2015', 3.82, 'The story of a super-secret spy organization that recruits an unrefined but promising street kid into the agency\'s ultra-competitive training program just as a global threat emerges from a twisted tech genius.', 431, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r6q9wZK5a2K51KFj4LWVID6Ja1r.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/1ZIeGwD2lMlLMr4u6IIR302jqhD.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Th_KrhqmHk8', 'Matthew Vaughn', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 1),
(451, 'City Hunter', '', '2024', 3.27, 'An exceptional marksman and hopeless playboy, private eye Ryo Saeba reluctantly forms an alliance with his late partner\'s sister to investigate his death.', 412, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cjQzJ9xFdaN9KAwu7HUImIgbc2Y.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/68afPR6EPV5wkE85whdO6al7FUx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G20m5NTAVAE', 'Yuichi Satoh', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 5, 7),
(452, 'The Mummy', 'La Mummia, Mummy, 木乃伊, 盗墓迷城, 미이라', '1999', 3.47, 'Dashing legionnaire Rick O\'Connell stumbles upon the hidden ruins of Hamunaptra while in the midst of a battle to claim the area in 1920s Egypt. It has been over three thousand years since former High Priest Imhotep suffered a fate worse than death as a punishment for a forbidden love—along with a curse that guarantees eternal doom upon the world if he is ever awoken.', 76616, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yhIsVvcUm7QxzLfT6HW2wLf5ajY.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/ygTSl89OtmXY4ESMpEF7qZcpGR8.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OGOBz4t7OXs', 'Stephen Sommers', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 8),
(453, 'Beauty and the Beast', 'Beauty and the Beast 2017, Bukuroshja dhe bisha, 美女與野獸(2017), 미녀와 야수', '1991', 3.50, 'A live-action adaptation of Disney\'s version of the classic tale of a cursed prince and a beautiful young woman who helps him break the spell.', 11417, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hKegSKIDep2ewJWPUQD7u0KqFIp.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/uU1Mt4JWhDvl4vKb3AfxNsorkoM.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0QwuPbbT_zk', 'Bill Condon', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 8),
(454, 'Scream VI', 'Blackmore', '2023', 3.50, 'Following the latest Ghostface killings, the four survivors leave Woodsboro behind and start a fresh chapter.', 3570, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wDWwtvkRRlgTiUr6TyLSMX8FCuZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/44immBwzhDVyjn87b3x3l9mlhAD.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Ie2qmAOc6Q', 'Matt Bettinelli-Olpin', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 3),
(455, 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles', 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 1, TMNT, 忍者龟：变种新任务, 닌자 터틀', '2014', 2.96, 'When a kingpin threatens New York City, a group of mutated turtle warriors must emerge from the shadows to protect their home.', 70549, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/azL2ThbJMIkts3ZMt3j1YgBUeDB.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/eezsbzYPbYKjjh6E1XHDBNlLynh.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dwXFsrp6WBs', 'Jonathan Liebesman', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 9),
(456, 'The Raffle', 'La Rifa, The Raffle, Φραντζέσκα, 라 리파', '1991', 3.35, 'Struggling with a financial crisis, a good-looking widow decides to put herself up for grabs. However, going through with it becomes almost impossible with a new love and the legal system thrown into the mix.', 25044, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Jc60w8ZemDMYqyJUStcQKy6syi.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/xGhwfRxTsP9VhDSNsfHqBcRvWKY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6SUwmv3UzpA', 'Francesco Laudadio', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 1, 10),
(457, 'Black Panther', 'Chiến Binh Báo Đen, Marvel\'s Black Panther, 黑豹, 마블 블랙 팬서', '2018', 3.69, 'King T\'Challa returns home to the reclusive, technologically advanced African nation of Wakanda to serve as his country\'s new leader. However, T\'Challa soon finds that he is challenged for the throne by factions within his own country as well as without. Using powers reserved to Wakandan kings, T\'Challa assumes the Black Panther mantle to join with ex-girlfriend Nakia, the queen-mother, his princess-kid sister, members of the Dora Milaje (the Wakandan \'special forces\') and an American secret agent, to prevent Wakanda from being dragged into a world war.', 40812, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uxzzxijgPIY7slzFvMotPv8wjKA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/b6ZJZHUdMEFECvGiDpJjlfUWela.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xjDjIWPwcPU', 'Ryan Coogler', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 5),
(458, 'Grown Ups', 'Copains pour toujours, Duze dzieci, Grandes personnes, 中坑同学会, 长大后', '2010', 3.20, 'After their high school basketball coach passes away, five good friends and former teammates reunite for a Fourth of July holiday weekend.', 81498, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cQGM5k1NtU85n4TUlrOrwijSCcm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/2q75qMwDijJPVbTp6SDDojjEEXg.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nk1ERmswxsY', 'Dennis Dugan', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 9),
(459, 'Luck', 'Suerte, حظ, 祝你好运', '2022', 3.89, 'Suddenly finding herself in the never-before-seen Land of Luck, the unluckiest person in the world must unite with the magical creatures there to turn her luck around.', 241, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1HOYvwGFioUFL58UVvDRG6beEDm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/sKvQUSyqsFq8e1ts6oo3Xp3dPH2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xSG5UX0EQVg', 'Peggy Holmes', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 9),
(460, 'Badland Hunters', 'Cazadores en Tierra Inhóspita, Wilderness, شکارچیان بدبوم, 荒野', '2024', 3.37, 'After a deadly earthquake turns Seoul into a lawless badland, a fearless huntsman springs into action to rescue a teenager abducted by a mad doctor.', 478, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sdI9ufheNPAKnWLl2hnsZKVk0EG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/pWsD91G2R1Da3AKM3ymr3UoIfRb.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7u3zBVAxx_w', 'Heo Myeong-haeng', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 6),
(461, 'Se7en', 'Pecados Capitales, Se7en - Os Sete Crimes Capitais, Seitse, Sev7n: Los siete pecados capitales, The Seven Deadly Sins', '1995', 4.19, 'Two homicide detectives are on a desperate hunt for a serial killer whose crimes are based on the \"seven deadly sins\" in this dark and haunting film that takes viewers from the tortured remains of one victim to the next. The seasoned Det. Sommerset researches each sin in an effort to get inside the killer\'s mind, while his novice partner, Mills, scoffs at his efforts to unravel the case.', 822, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6yoghtyTpznpBik8EngEmJskVUO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/vxPrxPufDQc4e2zr492LkXoEjdl.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vr3UZ-axauU', 'David Fincher', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 8),
(462, 'Gone Girl', 'Garota Exemplar, İtmiş Qız, Les apparences, เล่นซ่อนหาย, 失踪女孩', '2014', 3.95, 'With his wife\'s disappearance having become the focus of an intense media circus, a man sees the spotlight turned on him when it\'s suspected that he may not be innocent.', 408, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lv5xShBIDPe7m4ufdlV0IAc7Avk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/h2JaQWLKhapm7AuSViJwGiv8ngC.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-_-1nJf8Vg', 'David Fincher', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 5),
(463, 'Kalki 2898-AD', 'Kalki 2898 AD, Project K', '2024', 3.15, 'In the year 2898 AD, around 6000 years after Kurukshetra war, Ashwatthama gears up for his final battle of redemption at the sign of hope in a dystopian world and Bhairava, a wisecracking and self-interested bounty hunter, tired of the perilous life becomes the hurdle in the process.', 23097, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gAkT58p7lseg9s4gfFfV8azA7Z9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/wzPsJaZtMHjITNW93l6gw99T1u7.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rn7tdg6cpW4', 'Nag Ashwin', '2024-09-08 12:37:26', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 5);
