(464, 'The Intern', 'โก๋เก๋ากับบอสเก๋ไก๋, マイ・インターン：2015, 实习生', '2015', 3.61, '70-year-old widower Ben Whittaker has discovered that retirement isn\'t all it\'s cracked up to be. Seizing an opportunity to get back in the game, he becomes a senior intern at an online fashion site, founded and run by Jules Ostin.', 235, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9UoAC9tu8kIyRy8AcJnGhnH0gOH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/zFfaiMrOhWq8Tr95WEpMaG5znVo.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f6dKhzYgksc', 'Nancy Meyers', '2024-09-08 12:37:27', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 6),
