(493, 'The Boy in the Striped Pyjamas', 'Çizgili Pijamalı Çocuk, The Boy in the Striped Pajamas, The Boy in the Striped Pyjamas', '2008', 3.92, 'When his family moves from their home in Berlin to a strange new house in Poland, young Bruno befriends Shmuel, a boy who lives on the other side of the fence where everyone seems to be wearing striped pajamas. Unaware of Shmuel\'s fate as a Jewish prisoner or the role his own Nazi father plays in his imprisonment, Bruno embarks on a dangerous journey inside the camp\'s walls.', 2537, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sLwYSEVVV3r047cjrpRAbGgNsfL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/sIZQA3FrXdVR5E6M3ctrAqitiQS.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uwysOfnX2Qg', 'Mark Herman', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 7),
(494, 'How to Train Your Dragon', 'Ako vycvičiť draka, Draktränaren 1, Így neveld a sárkányodat 3D, 驯龙高手, 드래곤 길들이기 1', '2010', 3.92, 'As the son of a Viking leader on the cusp of manhood, shy Hiccup Horrendous Haddock III faces a rite of passage: he must kill a dragon to prove his warrior mettle. But after downing a feared dragon, he realizes that he no longer wants to destroy it, and instead befriends the beast – which he names Toothless – much to the chagrin of his warrior father.', 643, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/92olhXYaIX6lvB8jwFz4OSfPaKq.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/59vDC1BuEQvti24OMr0ZvtAK6R1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1huZhKwhIQc', 'Chris Sanders', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 7, 10),
(495, 'Real Steel', 'Gigantes de acero, Real Steel - Mein unschlagbarer Freund, Real Steel - Stahlharte Gegner, 鋼鐵擂台, 리얼 스틸', '2011', 3.51, 'Charlie Kenton is a washed-up fighter who retired from the ring when robots took over the sport. After his robot is trashed, he reluctantly teams up with his estranged son to rebuild and train an unlikely contender.', 81728, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4GIeI5K5YdDUkR3mNQBoScpSFEf.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/4f0Kj0QwPui5ydu1UavsnvP1m1o.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obYuPJH2oTE', 'Shawn Levy', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 8),
(496, 'Me, Myself & Irene', 'Az, moya milost i Aĭriĭn, Egó, aftí kai o eaftós mou, Futari no otoko to hitori no on\'na, Ja, ja i Irena, Me Myself and Irene', '2000', 3.30, 'Rhode Island State Trooper Charlie Baileygates has a multiple personality disorder. One personality is crazy and aggressive, while the other is more friendly and laid back. Both of these personalities fall in love with the same woman named Irene after Charlie loses his medication.', 31506, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rvRrcbLbpn7UJGRH1JupgHOeJFq.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/8qLen3NLCVSu1I9aqGWbTUIoBLQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JABG7viqJWc', 'Peter Farrelly', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 4, 4),
(497, 'Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice', 'Batman kontra Superman: Świt sprawiedliwości, Batman vs Superman El amanecer de la Justicia, Batman vs Superman: A Origem da Justiça, Betmen vs Supermen: Adolat boshlanish davrida, 배트맨 대 슈퍼맨: 저스티스의 시작', '2016', 2.99, 'Fearing the actions of a god-like Super Hero left unchecked, Gotham City’s own formidable, forceful vigilante takes on Metropolis’s most revered, modern-day savior, while the world wrestles with what sort of hero it really needs. And with Batman and Superman at war with one another, a new threat quickly arises, putting mankind in greater danger than it’s ever known before.', 141, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5UsK3grJvtQrtzEgqNlDljJW96w.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/5fX1oSGuYdKgwWmUTAN5MNSQGzr.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s9EkdAHqtvU', 'Zack Snyder', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 6, 4),
(498, 'Kaskasero', '', '2024', 3.00, 'A talented mechanic and driver, Migs quickly finds success when a customer he likes, Gabbi, leads him into the life of street car racing. But as he goes along this life and learns of Gabbi’s past, Migs makes rash decisions that might put the brakes on their relationship.', 72, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/veLIxyQJyXq8Lf6qSbXQl0ckHzC.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/aJxmgoNtP2BH7mRYvuf7AHB0VC3.jpg', NULL, 'Ludwig Peralta', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 2, 2),
(499, 'Zack Snyder\'s Justice League', 'Justice League: Director\'s Cut, Liga spravodlivosti Zacka Snydera, ザック・スナイダー版 ジャスティス・リーグ, 正义联盟导演剪辑版', '2021', 4.08, 'Determined to ensure Superman\'s ultimate sacrifice was not in vain, Bruce Wayne aligns forces with Diana Prince with plans to recruit a team of metahumans to protect the world from an approaching threat of catastrophic proportions.', 2469, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tnAuB8q5vv7Ax9UAEje5Xi4BXik.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/pcDc2WJAYGJTTvRSEIpRZwM3Ola.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ui37YKQ9AC4', 'Zack Snyder', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 8),
(500, 'Upgraded', 'Ascenso, Upgrade: Primera clase, Upgraded - Amore, arte e bugie, 升等之旅, 升舱巧遇', '2024', 3.64, 'Ana is an ambitious intern dreaming of a career in the art world while trying to impress her demanding boss Claire. When she\'s upgraded to first class on a work trip, she meets handsome Will, who mistakes Ana for her boss– a white lie that sets off a glamorous chain of events, romance and opportunity, until her fib threatens to surface.', 113, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4fKjh7zJrlAcZfIfNQCDvvrT5vN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280/77Fqz6PFCSnWySDOmEL6ZPcaYIl.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3_dj7BnHp8', 'Carlson Young', '2024-09-08 12:37:28', '2024-09-23 05:14:40', 1, 3, 1);
